Maan lijiye user ke paas 2 Applications hain:-
App A (Active Directory) — Isme user ke paas 2 Groups hain (VPN_Group, HR_Group).

App B (Salesforce) — Isme user ke paas Koi Group Nahi Hai (Null/Empty).

Aapke pichle code ka logic yeh tha:-
Aapne entitlements variable ko loop ke bilkul BAAHAR top par hi declare kar diya tha, kuch aise:-

List entitlements = null; // Memory mein ek hi dabba (variable) bana

for (Object link : links) { // Loop shuru hua
