❌ Galti 1: Cross-Contamination (Data ka Kichdi Banna)
Tumhare Galat Code Ka Tarika:
Tumne kya kiya, saare links ke loop mein ghuste hi atts.add(...) karke saare groups ek hi list mein bhar diye:-
Java
