Code Ke Sath Dekho Kya Hua:-
Maan lo user ke paas AD aur SAP do apps the. atts balti mein do items aaye: [memberOf: AD_Group, roles: SAP_Role].
Neeche jab tumhara loop chala, toh usne AD ke AccountRequest ke andar .add() kar diya:-
memberOf: AD_Group (Yeh sahi tha)
roles: SAP_Role (❌ Blunder! AD application ke andar roles aur SAP_Role naam ka koi attribute nahi hota).
Nuksaan: Jab SailPoint AD par yeh request bhejega, toh Active Directory crash ho jayegi aur error aayega:-"Attribute 'roles' is undefined for Active Directory".

❌ Galti 2: Cross-Multiplication (Loops ka Dhamaka):-
Tumhare Galat Code Ka Tarika:
Tumne entitlements ke loop ke andar new AccountRequest likha tha:-
